  "title": "Product Management Specialist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Identify opportunities to improve digital products—boost automation, reduce cost, and enhance client satisfaction.</li><li>Support the bank’s digital vision by helping shape innovative digital capabilities and solutions.</li><li>Assist in new product development and migration activities.</li><li>Coordinate and support UAT and BVT testing for new product releases.</li><li>Manage governance tasks and follow-ups with internal stakeholders.</li><li>Create and maintain process flows and SOPs to support smooth rollout and operations.</li><li>Oversee commercialization and migration activities, ensuring tasks are completed with relevant stakeholders.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Strong understanding of information technology and digital product development.</li><li>Experience in product management or related fields.</li><li>Good documentation and project coordination skills.</li><li>Ability to work with multiple stakeholders and follow through on tasks.</li></ul>",
